Moltres (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0145: Zapdos
Pokémon
#0147: Dratini →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Moltres (TCG Pocket).

Moltres has been featured on 28 different cards since it debuted in the Fossil expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Moltres cards are normally Fire-type, Colorless-type, or Darkness-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Moltres

Moltres
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
